metadata.name: Nara and Doragon.
metadata.description:
She Was Abandoned For Being Weak, But she had One OP AbilityI

she was transported to another world against her will.

she was  given a weak body that held everyone back to the point where she was left behind.

The world of dragons and demons. but she had to fight  against her will. but where she found one dragon. where they became close friends and the dragon guarded  her and help her to fight against the demons,

Soon thought they would learn how strong she really was.

She had to be strong, she had to work harder than anyone, she needs to always be on guard, she had to keep all the secrets sealed, but would all this be easy?

When a lot gets attracted to her without her trying, when a lot watches her closely because she's too
suspicious, when even her feelings that she made into stone are being melted.

She suddenly appeared in their kingdom 4 years ago. They didn't know who she was or where she came from. 

("THE BEGINNING") OF A NEW DAWN
